{"tid":1430943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武派可唔可以新增一系？","createTime":"2019-08-08T01:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:47:25.000Z","uid":259963,"like":5,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"51101358793af534ed245eca5db707ccae2c8904","tid":1430943,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:09:10.000Z","msg":"見到隔離po有爸打講勇武派分5系<br />\n1. 火系<br />\n2. 水系<br />\n3. 土系<br />\n4. 光系<br />\n5. 格鬥系<br />\n<br />\n上面咁多種都係以直接攻擊同傷害人身體而達致對方敗走<br />\n依種方法亦都係最消耗己方軍力，體力同物資嘅一種方法<br />\n<br />\n如果有種方法，成本又低，又可以拎到敵方自動敗走，唔需要埋身肉搏（但都阻止唔到敵方嘅遠程攻擊，但至少近身嘅打鬥可以避得就避啦），又有無得諗下？<br />\n<br />\n如果要大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">掟屎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n（又或者做屁彈，都係屎尿屁d野啦）又有無得諗？<br />\n<br />\n成本唔洗諗，self produce嘅野成本一定係最低<br />\n你諗下班狗成身gear都係屎，乜野士氣都無啦<br />\n仲用電筒照前線？睇住有無屎飛埋黎好過啦<br />\n又或者有可以運到一缸入去，用條喉加個電泵就直接噴出去，好過掟磚同掟石<br />\n加上，藍絲文宣可以收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔通話暴徒噴到英勇警察一身屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加埋張一身屎嘅警狗相，真係不得了<br />\n中立嘅人又唔會覺得暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以拉攏埋佢地去我地依邊<br />\n真係一舉幾得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但依個方法都有限制<br />\n<br />\n1. 鬧市會超級擾民（我諗程度僅次於催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我建議係元朗白衫陣地附近用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n2. 前線嘅嗅覺一定要麻木曬<br />\n<br />\n3. 事後要自發洗街（而家都有完結後執垃圾嘅義工隊，依個問題未必好大，解決水源問題就足夠）<br />\n<br />\n4. 依樣野做得唔好嘅話，會令人覺得成件事好鳩而抗拒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以要定立一個好確切嘅目標（eg我們不是暴徒！，沒有流血抗爭！等等）令人覺得我地依個舉動係升級左，唔似班狗淨係識打人<br />\n<br />\n依樣做得好可以帶民意！<br />\n<br />\n因為腳有缺陷，無上過前線唔想拖累人只可以做冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有諗得唔夠全面嘅請大家幫手比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee0ca17e65de2d60f0526b70838e293cdb60c39","tid":1430943,"uid":298077,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:10:57.000Z","msg":"事後要自發洗街<br />\non9 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911e11e17138c7b3309f88a5e05c8237555efb8f","tid":1430943,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:11:09.000Z","msg":"前4系都係格鬥系黎喎"},{"pid":"493fbf07eeb30329ea51c7e26743c89298a9f4e8","tid":1430943,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:12:56.000Z","msg":"比屎好嘅野太多"},{"pid":"21eabd4431f478d53723d662afc42731a767e164","tid":1430943,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ee0ca17e65de2d60f0526b70838e293cdb60c39","tid":1430943,"uid":298077,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:10:57.000Z","msg":"事後要自發洗街<br />\non9 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"但而家都有人幫手執乾淨條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fde91752fe2871286e08214fdbbecae65730ea1","tid":1430943,"uid":74096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:13:45.000Z","msg":"你唔好話扔m巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0924d2a24aeb13c56a85f7583e66c8dd989fe9","tid":1430943,"uid":53003,"like":1,"